summary: A hidden player house located in the Sleeping Giant Inn in Riverwoood (there is a trapdoor in one off the sleeping rooms off the inn)
descriptionHtml:
A hidden player house located in the Sleeping Giant Inn in Riverwoood (there is a trapdoor in one off the sleeping rooms off the inn).

There is a Forge, Armor workbench, Weapon sharpening thingy, Enchanting table, Alchemy table, Coocking spit, 3 training dummies, Bed, Eating table, World map with flags, Altar, Wardrobe it is navmeshed so youre followers will follow you in.
author: zombiecake44
